 radiatively accelerated. These results suggest that at a sufficiently\nlarge radial distance there is a break point between MHD-dominated and\nradiatively driven outflows.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Oct 2016 16:06:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Oct 2016 18:07:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-21"}
