a material. The\ncomparison of predicted and observed Ne and O spectral line ratios reveals no\nsigns of strong Ne enhancement and suggests the progenitor is a CO white dwarf.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Oct 2016 16:09:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-07"}
