type of anti-patterns). Therefore, developers\nshould consider the impact on energy efficiency of refactoring when applying\nmaintenance activities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Oct 2016 17:18:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Oct 2016 22:20:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-21"}
