s of the\nenergetic particles it accelerated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Oct 2016 20:20:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 4 Dec 2016 17:07:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-28"}
