ed with the local pattern topology is\nhomeomorphic to the space of subshifts. This yields a useful tool to analyze\nthese systems. Furthermore, it delivers the connection of the existence of\nperiodic orbits in a subshift of finite type and the existence of periodic\napproximations for subshifts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Oct 2016 07:39:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-20"}
