^2$-estimates for these conical square functions hold. This opens the door to\nthe study of weighted and unweighted Hardy spaces and of boundary value\nproblems associated with $L_w$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Oct 2016 10:36:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Oct 2016 09:44:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 27 Jun 2017 10:38:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-13"}
