l the three compounds, which shall certainly pave\nguidance to future experimental work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Oct 2016 14:37:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Oct 2016 08:47:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-21"}
